<section xml:id="section-general-users">
<title>(1.1) General Users</title>
<simpara>The very first thing that every akaun-platform users would need to have, is to sign up for and AkaunID. You can do so by visiting <link xl:href="https://akaun.com/">https://akaun.com/</link></simpara>
<section xml:id="_your_akaunid">
<title>Your AkaunID</title>
<simpara>It is important for you to understand that with a single AkaunID, it is possible for you to have multiple Sign-In methods. You could be using an email with password, a phone number with the same password, you could also be adding access keys to your AkaunID for integration purposes.</simpara>
</section>
